    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I don't understand the reason this function is exported outside the package. If you kept it internal, then it would only be called from `init()` and you wouldn't need the `testSemaphoreMu`.\n\nI don't really think it is safe to call outside `init()` anyway, since a goroutine might have already acquired the semaphore, so the release would be against a different channel.",
